OL,3,CMessi fans complain after World Cup
OL,4,Cwinner fails to play in Hong Kong
OL,5,Cfriendly
OL,7,Fhas gone from hero to zero in after
OL,8,Fthe Argentine failed to take to the
OL,9,Fpitch in an Inter Miami showcase game
OL,10,Fstaged in the city.
OL,12,FThe World Cup winner was supposed to
OL,13,Fbe the star of the show in the
OL,14,Ffriendly game against Hong Kong XI,
OL,15,Fbut both he and Luis Suarez - the
OL,16,Fteam's two biggest stars - stayed on
OL,17,Fthe bench.
