OL,5,Cfriendly
OL,7,FAs Inter Miami left the field
OL,8,Ffollowing their 4-1 win, chants of
OL,9,F"refund, refund" could be heard from
OL,10,Fthe crowd, and club owner David
OL,11,FBeckham was booed during his post-
OL,12,Fmatch speech.
OL,14,FAfter arriving in Hong Kong, the World
OL,15,FCup winner was mobbed by adoring fans
OL,16,Fwho camped out at the team hotel,
OL,17,Fwearing the blue and white of
OL,18,FArgentina or the pink strip of Inter
OL,19,FMiami.
