OL,5,Cfriendly
OL,7,FTens of thousands flocked to the
OL,8,Fstadium for a training session ahead
OL,9,Fof the Saturday night match, and
OL,10,Fchanted "Messi, Messi, Messi" as he
OL,11,Fand Beckham played with a group of
OL,12,Flocal school children.
OL,14,FTickets for the game went on sale in
OL,15,FDecember and sold out almost
OL,16,Fimmediately, with some Messi fans
OL,17,Fpaying up to #500 to see him playing
OL,18,Fin Hong Kong for the first time since
OL,19,F2014.
