OL,3,CMessi fans complain after World Cup
OL,4,Cwinner fails to play in Hong Kong
OL,5,Cfriendly
OL,7,FThe Hong Kong government put out a
OL,8,Fstatement following the game
OL,9,Fexpressing "deep disappointment over
OL,10,FMessi not playing" and at the
OL,11,Forganisers for failing to provide a
OL,12,Fdetailed explanation promptly.
OL,14,FOn Monday, the secretary for Culture,
OL,15,FSports and Tourism revealed that there
OL,16,Fhad been an agreement with the
OL,17,Forganisers that Messi must participate
OL,18,Fin the game for at least forty-five
OL,19,Fminutes, subject to fitness and safety
OL,20,Fconsiderations.
