OL,5,Cfriendly
OL,7,FWhen the second half began without the
OL,8,Fplayer having taken to the field, the
OL,9,Forganisers were told to speak to Inter
OL,10,FMiami bosses and arrange for Messi to
OL,11,Fplay as soon as possible.
OL,13,FThey were later told that he was
OL,14,Finjured. A final request was made for
OL,15,Fhim to come on at the end and interact
OL,16,Fwith fans and accept the trophy, but
OL,17,Fthe organisers were informed Messi was
OL,18,Funable to take part.
