OL,7,FIt is clear head coach Gerardo Martino
OL,8,Fhad no intention of playing Messi or
OL,9,FSuarez in the game, admitting
OL,10,Fafterwards that the pair have injuries
OL,11,Fthat he did not want to aggravate.
OL,13,FOutside the stadium a fan angrily
OL,14,Fkicked a cardboard cut-out of Messi,
OL,15,Fand many fans took to social media to
OL,16,Fexpress their anger.
