OL,4,Cwinner fails to play in Hong Kong
OL,5,Cfriendly
OL,7,FThe government has criticised Inter
OL,8,FMiami for its handling of the
OL,9,Fsituation, and not telling fans in
OL,10,Fgood time that the star they had come
OL,11,Fto see would not take to the field.
OL,13,FInter Miami are continuing their Asia
OL,14,Ftour with a trip to Tokyo, where they
OL,15,Fwill play another pre-season friendly
OL,16,Fon Wednesday.
OL,18,FFans in Japan who had been preparing
OL,19,Ffor Messi mania, are now preparing
OL,20,Fthemselves to share in Hong Kong's
OL,21,FMessi misery.
